{"tid":1288286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中共初心) 毛澤東: 自由民主的中國, 將是這樣的一個國家","createTime":"2019-07-05T14:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T14:57:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1183fc629166e11cb95134873ac79c63fdf05585","tid":1288286,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/baotong1932/status/1147029955869458432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbaotong1932%2Fstatus%2F1147029955869458432&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=198dd034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbaotong1932%2Fstatus%2F1147029955869458432&h=f7558ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/baotong1932/status/1147029955869458432</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;自由民主的中國將是這樣的一個國家，它的各級政府直至中央政府都由普遍、平等、無記名的選舉所產生，並向選舉它的人民負責。它將實現孫中山先生的三民主義，林肯的民有、民治、民享的原則與羅斯福的四大自由。&rdquo;（中央文獻研究室編：《毛澤東文集》第四卷，人民出版社，1996年，第27、28頁）。"},{"pid":"4b60e84c2e0ad7defa172a66ec18cbb32aa3515b","tid":1288286,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"順便講, 連登仔唔駛再盲學毛澤東攪革命<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東後來推翻國民黨政權， 主要因為兩大原因：<br />\n1） 蘇聯向中共提供大量軍事援助與裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/26/830123.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F830123.html&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=a50a0cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/26/830123.html</a><br />\n2） 美國很早便決定放棄支持國民黨<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/amlink/26024716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Famlink%2F26024716&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=4688149e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/amlink/26024716</a>"},{"pid":"636e12debff82bc5773db2b02b7c60d131acb22d","tid":1288